title: American stars face stiff test from each other
text: > Sports American stars face stiff test from each other FILE - In this Sept. 12, 2015, file photo, U.S. gymnast Aly Raisman trains at the Karolyi Ranch in New Waverly, Texas. The U.S. women's gymnastics team should stroll through qualifying at the world championships on Saturday. Yet one of the three Americans who will compete in the all-around _ defending Olympic champion Gabby Douglas, two-time world champ Simone Biles or three-time Olympic medalist Aly Raisman _ will have to watch the all-around finals from the stands thanks to the rules that limit each country to two competitors in the finals. (AP Photo/David J. Phillip, File)
